title: Cisco Meraki: Wireless ethernet statuses
agents: cisco_meraki
catalog: os/services
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check plug-in monitors wireless ethernet statuses.

 In order to make this check plug-in work, you have to configure the ruleset for
 the special agent {{Cisco Meraki}} to include the "Wireless ethernet statuses"
 section.

discovery:
 One service per organisation ID and device serial is created.
